## Design guidelines

### Logo

png

![logoBlack.png](attachment:e7d417b7-35f5-4fb4-8eaf-c1d5118b564f:logoBlack.png)

![logoWhite.png](attachment:f5cf500a-7b47-4b96-bbeb-5bff163355e2:logoWhite.png)

